name: Rak  (rebel)
content:
Rak was a human male soldier for the Alliance to Restore the Republic. During the Galactic Civil War between the Alliance and the Galactic Empire, he fought Imperial troops on the moon Jedha.
Rak was a human male who joined the Alliance to Restore the Republic sometime during or before the year 0 BBY.
Rak was a human with black eyes and dark skin.
Rak wore the fatigues of a Rebel trooper.
Rak was created as a playable character for the online browser video game Star Wars: Boots on the Ground. Players could select Rak to be a member of their three-man rebel squad. The image used for the character in Boots on the Ground is also an image of Taidu Sefla from Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.
